    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors and determined that the CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for the intended COU. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The team declared High assurance based on the overall positive validation outcomes and close agreement with experimental hemolysis data across all operating points. The discretization error factor was judged adequate based on qualitative mesh comparison.",
